headline: C.H. Robinson is the disruptor, 'not the disrupted': CEO
summary: Logistics company C.H. Robinson (CHRW) saw a steep decline in its stock prices last week after a new freight-shipping AI tool announced by Algorhythm Holdings (RIME) sparked a wider sell-off in the transportation sector (^DJT). C.H. Robinson CEO Dave Bozeman joins Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi for a conversation about the company's broader view on last week's stock reaction and where C.H. Robinson still stands in the transportation industry. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Opening Bid.
